{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji52.pdf"],"article":{"title":"七律·雷电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七律·雷电积云忽作闷雷声，雨弹光刀欲杀人。岂向瑶台追幻梦，还从烈火识真金。几枝玉叶化灰蝶，再度铁梅成赤心。稳似泰山同携手，陶然一笑友情深。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":217,"page_end":217},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}